com.i2group.apollo.externaldata.transport

Class ItemGroup

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.i2group.apollo.externaldata.transport.ItemGroup

  • public final class ItemGroup
extends Object
    A container for information about a group of Items and ItemPlaceholders that appear in the results of a call to an external data retrieval or subset exploration service method. The identifier of an ItemGroup matches the identifier of the ProvenanceGroup to which the results correspond.
    Since:
    4.0
